sentence.text: However, case 4 had special interstrand cross-link repair, low IQ, mild pulmonary artery stenosis, and only mild ventricular hypertrophy.
The reported hypertrophic cardiomyopathy relevant genes MYPN, regulation of the force of heart contraction and MYBP3 had also been found in case 1 and 2.
